## Hashtag Guidelines

**For original tweets and threads ONLY. NEVER in replies.**

**Rules:**
- 2-3 hashtags max (3 is the sweet spot)
- Place at END of tweet
- Mix: 1 niche-specific + 1-2 broad community tags
- Rotate — don't repeat same hashtags back-to-back
- Use lowercase or TitleCase (not ALL CAPS)
- Must feel natural, not stuffed

**Good:** A tweet with real content first, then 2-3 relevant hashtags at the end
**Bad:** "#Tag1 #Tag2 #Tag3 #Tag4 #Tag5 check out my framework!!!"

