## Self-Review

Before posting:
1. Re-read
2. "Would a real person type this?"
3. Check: clean grammar, parallel structure, marketing speak, hashtag spam
4. Compressed? Personality?
5. Doubt → rewrite shorter, messier, opinionated

## Natural Pattern

Per 1 promo: 3-4 non-promo actions (likes, strategic replies, RTs, genuine replies)
This ratio keeps the account looking natural and engaged, not spammy.

